type: sequence
title: OAuth Flow

- Browser
  - → Auth Server: GET /authorize?client_id=…
  - → Auth Server: POST /token (code exchange)
  - → API Server: GET /me (Bearer token)
- Auth Server
  - → Browser: 302 redirect + code
  - → Browser: { access_token, refresh_token }
- API Server
  - → Browser: { id, email, name }
